2 Cf. for example Cassirer, Philosophic der Symbolischen Formen, III, Chap. VI, 
Pathologie des Symbolbewusstseins. 

s One can indeed imagine an intellectualist interpretation of schizophrenia 
which would equate the atomistic conception of time and the loss of the future 
with a collapse of the categorial attitude. 

